  <summary date="2022-12-02T20:55:33Z" status="Introduced in House">Fallen Heroes Flag Reauthorization Act of 2022

This bill reauthorizes through FY2027 a program through which a Member of Congress may provide, at no cost, a Capitol-flown flag to commemorate a firefighter, law enforcement officer, or other public safety officer who died in the line of duty if an immediate family member of the deceased requests such a flag.</summary>
